<br>
If you were a big, badass mob with a gazillion hps, the ability to take down any pc that isn't being healed with 3-6 blows, and spells and resistance to magic up the wazoo, which is likely to bother you more? <br>
<br>
1. A guy hitting you 50 times a minute with the equivilent damage of a salad fork...<br>
<br>
2. A guy carving out large chunks of your flesh 2 times a minute with some nasty high damage weapon...<br>
<br>
This isn't meant to be a discussion of the merits of any class over another. This is just a discussion purely about &quot;does this make any sense to you?&quot; IE why does a very low damage very fast weapon gain agro better than a high damage slower weapon with a higher dps.<br>
